  m_Name: Fairies
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::CreatureData
  creatureName: Fairies
  image: {fileID: 10905, guid: 0000000000000000f000000000000000, type: 0}
  description: 'Fairies are mischievous little creatures. They often take the form
    of small beautiful women, but can also take the form of frogs, insects or simply
    be invisible. They are the fog over the field at dawn and dusk, this is the magical
    time where they like to dance. Be careful to join them, you may go mad or only
    escape from the dance when years or decades have passed.

    Fairies hold grudges,
    or sometimes feel a little evil. They blow sickness on humans. '
